  <lyrics>
    <stanza type="verse" number="">Siya maluloy-on,
Mahigugmaon,
Nag-antus' kasakit
Alang kanato.
Namatay didto's krus
Alang's sala ta;
Cristo Manluluwas,
Unsay buhaton mo?</stanza>
  </lyrics>
</hymn>
